CLEARMETHOD
PRERUNPROGRAM 1
POSTRUNPROGRAM 0
ENABLEACQUISITION 1
ENABLEANALYSIS 1
CUSTOMANALYSIS 1
COPYMETHOD 0
SAVEGLPDATA 0
PRERUNNAME "macro _automspath$+""msautosn.mac"""
