SIGNAL2METH ""
ANALYSISMACRO "auto_sn -1,,""Reserpine-1956SL"""
METHODCOMMENT
METHODCOMMENT "Reserpine SIM Method for G1956 SL Model"
METHODCOMMENT "APCI Positive Ion Sensitivity Test\"
